      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, approved\n\nPatch is fine.\n\nIf it needs to be resubmitted, it could be improved by changing the comment for the obsolete OBD_MD_FLMDT_IDX by including the version this flag was removed, or if it was never used in the network protocol at all. This will make it easier to decide when the flag can be reused.",
