      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nPlease also remove \"OBD_MD_MDTIDX\" from the file of  lustre/utils/wirecheck.c\n\nAnd add \"MF_GET_MDT_IDX\" checking in the file of  lustre/utils/wirecheck.c\n\nAnd re-generate wiretest.c",
